description:
ONLY FOR FLASH ENABLED DEVICES.
NEEDS BING MAPS UPDATE (this app is coded with Enyo Framework)

Flash Game catalog brings together a large number of flash games for the HP Pre2. Take advantage of flash technology in webOS. Access a list of flash games tested on HP Pre2 by users of this application. (50+ games tested for now, number growing every weeks).

Features : Create game shortcut in the webOS launcher. 

All games are free and ad supported during game load.

Better FPS with overclocked devices
